*(''condition of a system in which competing influences are balanced''): [[balance]], [[stability]]
*(''in physics''):
*(''in chemistry''):
*(''mental balance''): [[sanity]]

====Antonyms====
*(''condition of a system in which competing influences are balanced''): [[disequilibrium]], [[instability]], [[unbalance]]
*(''in physics''): [[disequilibrium]]
*(''in chemistry''):
*(''mental balance''): [[insanity]], [[instability]], [[madness]]

